     <div class="Varieties"> 
        <h3 style=" font-size: 30px; text-align: left; color: white;"><strong><i>VARIETIES:</i></strong></h3>
        <p style="color: white;font-size: 20px;"><strong><i>1.<u>Jammu and Kashmir</u>:</i></strong> Golden Delicious (Late Season), Lal Ambri, Mollies Delicious, Starkrimson, Red June, Irish Peach, Benoni and Tydeman’s Early<br>

